extends ../layout

block content
  .container-fluid
    .row(class='align-items-center',style='border-top: 5px solid black; padding-top: 5px')
      .col(class='bcontent')
        h1.title PORTFOLIO - FPG SALES PORTAL
        #carouselExampleIndicators.carousel.slide(data-ride='carousel')
          ol.carousel-indicators
            li.active(data-target='#carouselExampleIndicators', data-slide-to='0')
            li(data-target='#carouselExampleIndicators', data-slide-to='1')
            li(data-target='#carouselExampleIndicators', data-slide-to='2')
          .carousel-inner
            .carousel-item.active
              img.d-block.w-100(src='../images/portifolio/frewprocess/Dashboard2.png', alt='Dashboard page')
              div(class='carousel-caption d-none d-md-block')
              h4 Dashboard
              h5 When an employee signs into the portal they land on to this dashboard page that give them a glance look at the company's progress categorized by certain documents. The is also filter functionality that enables a historical data search.
            .carousel-item
              img.d-block.w-100(src='../images/portifolio/frewprocess/Dashboard.png', alt='Dashboard page')
              div(class='carousel-caption d-none d-md-block')
              h4 Dashboard (continued)
              h5 The graphs have interactive functionality that enables a user to click the original graph and be presented the a graph that responds to clicks and mouseover hovers.
            .carousel-item
              img.d-block.w-100(src='../images/portifolio/frewprocess/Sales Goals.png', alt='Sales goals page')
              div(class='carousel-caption d-none d-md-block')
              h4 Sales Goals
              h5 This page allows a user to create sales target goals based on different sales territories and also to filter and search those goals.
            .carousel-item
              img.d-block.w-100(src='../images/portifolio/frewprocess/Customer Accounts.png', alt='Customer Accounts page')
              div(class='carousel-caption d-none d-md-block')
              h4 Customer Accounts
              h5 The Customer Accounts page list all customers that the company has and provides options to select if a customer is a sales target for a particular period or not. It also provides searching and sorting capabilities.
            .carousel-item
              img.d-block.w-100(src='../images/portifolio/frewprocess/Prospects Map.png', alt='Prospects Map page')
              div(class='carousel-caption d-none d-md-block')
              h4 Prospects Map
              h5 The Prospects map page displays plotted customers by different categorization( target account, key accounts, and historic customers and others) which ties back to sales efforts roles assigned on the Customer Accounts page. This page leverages to googleMaps API. On a customer point a user is able to see the customer's past orders and past paid invoices. The right fly out enable filtering by date, classifications, categories, account type, geocoding quality, and by dynamically adding some grouped filters. Last but not least a user can short list the customers that they want to focus on by doubling clicking on a customer point and adding the to the "Added Partners" cache.
            .carousel-item
              img.d-block.w-100(src='../images/portifolio/frewprocess/Customizable Map.png', alt='Customizable Map page')
              div(class='carousel-caption d-none d-md-block')
              h4 Prospects Map (continued)
              h5 The Customizable Map is were the "Added Partners" from the Prospects Map are displayed. On this page a user can search a customer's address straight on to the maps and can added on the points to be able to print the information.
            .carousel-item
              img.d-block.w-100(src='../images/portifolio/frewprocess/Upload.png', alt='Customizable Map page')
              div(class='carousel-caption d-none d-md-block')
              h4 Prospects Map (continued)
              h5 The Upload page is for uploading excel marketing data into the company's database. This follows a number of different business rules to ensure data integrity. Before uploading a file users can verify if their excel document is formatted correctly by downloading a copy of the excepted file format.
          a.carousel-control-prev(href='#carouselExampleIndicators', role='button', data-slide='prev')
              span.carousel-control-prev-icon(aria-hidden='true')
              span.sr-only Previous
          a.carousel-control-next(href='#carouselExampleIndicators', role='button', data-slide='next')
            span.carousel-control-next-icon(aria-hidden='true')
            span.sr-only Next
